text: The 1916 Argentine Primera División was the 25th season of top-flight football in Argentina. The season began on March 23 and ended on December.Argentina 1916 by Osvaldo Gorgazzi at RSSSF.com Racing Club win its 4th consecutive league championship. == Final standings == ==References== Category:Argentine Primera División seasons Category:1916 in Argentine football Category:1916 in South American football
